    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1735034684\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About The Game.</strong></h2><br>100 Dogs - The goal of the game is to find dogs! The game has several levels and various musical accompaniment that will not get bored.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.poster.avif?t=1735034684\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.webm?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.mp4?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Someone will say - &quot;Nah, it's easy&quot;.</strong></h2><br>Think everything is simple? Some of the dogs are really well hidden, so if you complete all the levels without hints, it will be amazing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.poster.avif?t=1735034684\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.webm?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.mp4?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leeeevels.</strong></h2><br>Make your way through the labyrinths of cleverly hidden levels full of surprises and puzzles. Explore a wide variety of places - from busy city streets to mysterious forests and abandoned ruins. Each new location presents unexpected challenges and much more.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>City<br></li><li>Western<br></li><li>Coming soon<br></li><li>Super Coming soon<br></li><li>Mega Coming soon<br></li><li>(And so on)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.poster.avif?t=1735034684\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.webm?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.mp4?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1735034684\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1735034684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057380/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d37